public class CalculatorTest
extends junit.framework.TestCase

Tests for the calculator class Tests the validate function by testing each possible output multiple times. Tests the success of the validation Test the output of the calculations by performing the same calculation using the medusa website (http://www.injguide.nhs.uk/), recording the results and testing against the results found. Drug of each equation type (pateint weight and time, just time and just patient weight) has been selected for testing.

Authors:
Aidan Wynne Fewster
